binary#!#varbinary
<NULL>#!#<NULL>
0000000000#!#3132333435
0000000000#!#3132333435
00000004D2#!#00003039
3132333400#!#00
3132333400#!#
3132333400#!#3132333435
3132333435#!#31323334353637383940
~~END~~


